Note: documentation is under construction. 

-----------------------
BASIC USAGE
----------------------
$(document.ready(function(){
    $(".toggle_field").toggleForms();
});

Where each form input has the class toggle_field. This will create a default button with the text "edit".

--------------------
OPTIONS
-------------------
buttonClass - this class will be added to each of the buttons. Use it to stylize the autogenerated buttons.
valueClass - this class will be added to each of the HTML values. 
buttonText- text to be displayed inside the button. set to "" if you want to use an icon instead (with a button class ofcourse)


